{
  "stem": "7458.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least for the moment, we were grateful we were under Soviet occupation and not in the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, many people felt that this is too good to be true and it would end, as indeed it did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It was really-- I remember very clearly on a weekend-- it was, I think, a Saturday morning-- my niece, who was three years younger than I, Roske, and I went into the fields to gather flowers and to play.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think I mentioned that, by that time, we lived on the outskirts of town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a larger house, a tannery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had some fields behind the tannery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We actually had two ponds with fish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember going swimming there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had woods not far-- in back of the fields, the woods started, which eventually played an important part in our surviving.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And on that Saturday morning-- it was June 21st, 1941-- Roske and I were in the field, gathering flowers, when suddenly we heard planes coming.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we saw the planes come quite low over the town, and we heard explosions.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Bombs were falling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We ran home to find out that Germany attacked the Soviet Union-- without warning, of course-- and started the war against the Soviet Union, and the bombs were being dropped on the Minski factory, which was an important leather factory, producing leather for the Soviet army.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so that was when the horror of the Holocaust began, really.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, it took the Germans-- again, with Blitzkrieg-- only a few days to demolish the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The Russian army was certainly better equipped than the Polish army, but they were no match for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were disorganized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Thousands and thousands were taken captive.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
